    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The decision was made by the finance team and the CTO together, so it's not something an individual can just override. They've already run the projections and decided the cost savings from the template system outweigh the \"nuance\" you're talking about. Honestly, the templates are way more reliable for them because they don't hallucinate or get too wordy. It's just business.",
